      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into perfection with this absolute gem! This vehicle is in mint condition, looking and driving just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. Every detail is flawless, from the pristine exterior to the immaculate interior\u2014truly a rare find for the most discerning buyer!",
