      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of unparalleled distinction. This specimen has been curated to an exacting standard, exhibiting a condition that satisfies the most discerning automotive enthusiast. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a rigorous commitment to preservation. This is an investment-grade offering for those who demand uncompromising excellence and a showroom-quality experience.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
